            <scopecontent id="aspace_e988ed219a907be6446dc73ea44d7d42">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Writings contains articles about St. Luke's Hospice/Palliative Care Program, articles by members of the hospice team, and a transcript and tapes from an oral history dictated by Patrice O'Connor and Rev. Carleton Sweetser. Writings by hospice team members cover many topics relevant to St. Luke's Hospice/Palliative Care Program and to the hospice movement in general.</p>
            </scopecontent>
